    <h1>Underwater <span>Welding</span></h1>
    <p class="page-hero-sub">One of the highest-paying and highest-risk specializations in the industry — combining commercial diving with structural welding on subsea platforms, pipelines, and hulls.</p>
    <div class="page-meta">
      <span class="page-meta-item">Pay: <strong>$60K–$150K+/yr</strong></span>
      <span class="page-meta-item">Path: <strong>Diver + Welder combined</strong></span>
